&lt;p&gt;Physician Associate Internship&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;AFC Band 6 (£31,365 - £37,890)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has become available to work as a Physician Associate Intern at the Dudley Group. The successful candidate will spend 6 months in ED and 6 months in Acute Medicine.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will join an existing team of 17 Physician Associates across Russells Hall Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Furthermore, the post holder will work within multi-disciplinary teams with a view to contribute in service improvement projects within the Trust. The chosen candidate will be supported in developing their knowledge and skills across the aforementioned specialties. The successful candidate will possess a Post Graduate Diploma or MSc in Physician Associate Studies from one of the UK Physician Associate Programmes, and have successfully passed the National Exam whilst also on the PA Managed Voluntary Register (PAMVR). &lt;strong&gt;Only qualified PAs or PAs that have sat their national exams and awaiting results should apply&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants are advised to apply early as if a large number of applications are received for this post we reserve the right to close the vacancy prior to the advertised date.&lt;/p&gt;
